data.description: Well priced home in great location close to Holy Family Church/School, Hospital, shopping. Enclosed front porch, 3 Season room with French doors off living room. Large kitchen with Oak cabinetry, tile floor, and pantry. Remodeled bath, vinyl plank floor, ceramic tile shower, newer vanity. Deck, patio, fenced yard, and 2 car garage. Replacement windows and newer furnace. Strictly "AS-IS" sale. Investor owner has never lived in or visited the property since purchase in 2017.
